{"tid":1559353,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【中秋佳節】無論你身處何方 都不會孤單。","createTime":"2019-09-10T18:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T07:31:56.000Z","uid":200288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eda9ca3f95c907d2ba76eacd3ab68d392fab4b2f","tid":1559353,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話咁快就中秋啦<br />\n 相信廣大市民 可能都會放低緊張低落既情緒 <br />\n去唔同嘅地方<br />\n［公園、球場、燒烤場、甚至網吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />］<br />\n共渡花好月圓中秋夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然當日可能有兄弟爬山 咁就睇情況各有各做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果當晚大家一切安好 前往慶祝節日 懇請廣大<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港</span></span>市民 於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">十時正</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">高叫口號</span></span> 然後於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">十點零五分</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">高舉手機燈光唱國歌</span></span> 以表達我地所有人嘅愛國情懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讓中秋夜響起屬於香港人嘅聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊個 響邊個 呢個中夜唔會再係毒撚一個<br />\n因為有香港人陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9ba303e73083ffedcf9af8af40c104605c8b9796","tid":1559353,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" 